    <briefdescription>
<para>Configuration structure for the Scene Change Detection IP core. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This structure contains the configuration parameters for the Xilinx Scene Change Detection video processing IP. It includes device identification, memory addressing, format support settings, and resource constraints.</para><para><simplesect kind="note"><para>The structure uses conditional compilation (SDT - Scoped Device Tree) to support both legacy and device tree based configurations. </para></simplesect>
</para>    </detaileddescription>
